{"tid":36873,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[成波之路]拿破崙意粉 (圖文+影片食譜)","createTime":"2016-12-13T03:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T15:26:58.000Z","uid":35319,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"352fa519271044febcffd593be7512782adf8cc6","tid":36873,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:56:25.000Z","msg":"影片：<a href=\"http://youtu.be/_EdBdvpvcxY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_EdBdvpvcxY&d=Y7aFt8csvxidpS%2FVU3tnGGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d212b2b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/_EdBdvpvcxY</a><br />\n<br />\n呢種意粉同拿破崙一啲關係都無<br />\n傳說呢個做法係二戰果陣，日本一間酒店既大廚煮畀美軍個大粒佬食，然後個食譜再流傳到民間<br />\n而又因為打完仗無啖好食，日本人將蕃茄改成茄汁，然後改下改下就變到而家咁<br />\n真唔真都好啦，整呢個意粉又平又快又好味係真嘅，無呃你！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61Gc22e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61Gc22e.jpg&h=a54235b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFacebook:\t<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/mywaystogetfat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmywaystogetfat&d=Y7aFt8csvxidpS%2FVU3tnGGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=f0676d1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/mywaystogetfat</a><br />\nInstagram:\t<a href=\"http://instagram.com/mywaystogetfat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fmywaystogetfat&d=Y7aFt8csvxidpS%2FVU3tnGGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ca12817c\" target=\"_blank\">http://instagram.com/mywaystogetfat</a><br />\nBlog:\t\t<a href=\"http://www.mywaystogetfat.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mywaystogetfat.com&d=Y7aFt8csvxidpS%2FVU3tnGGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=f0424ad7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mywaystogetfat.com</a><br />\n<strong>Blog 可以睇返之前出過post既食譜</strong><br />\n有興趣請like/follow/睇睇啦，多謝你既留意同支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d449550f0fbaea1bd3381952d37a77392a55db2d","tid":36873,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5221e1ac1bd24a7da420dbc154feb4dba7cbd71a","tid":36873,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>份量：2 &ndash; 3 人<br />\n<ins>材料</ins></strong>\t<br />\n意粉\t200 克<br />\n洋蔥\t100 克<br />\n火腿\t80 克<br />\n甘筍\t40 克<br />\n青椒\t40 克<br />\n蒜頭\t3 瓣<br />\n鰹魚粉\t2 茶匙<br />\n茄汁\t6 湯匙<br />\n糖\t2湯匙<br />\n巴馬臣芝士粉\t2 湯匙<br />\n<br />\n1. 首先煮滾一大鍋水。<br />\n把洋蔥、火腿、甘筍和青椒切絲。蒜頭壓成蓉備用。<br />\n水滾後加少許鹽，下意粉，按包裝指示的時間減去 2 分鐘煮熟意粉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/40m6jvf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40m6jvf.jpg&h=c567f93b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n2. 煮意粉的同時，以中火燒鐵鍋子，下少許油，油熱後下洋蔥炒約 3 分鐘至軟身。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6v6omV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6v6omV.jpg&h=ec0297c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n3. 下火腿、甘筍和青椒同炒 1 &ndash; 2 分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1A88L42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1A88L42.jpg&h=b3439167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 下蒜蓉同炒 1 &ndash; 2 分鐘至有香氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N53xO0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN53xO0A.jpg&h=462b415b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 意粉煮夠時間後，先留下 2 湯匙煮意粉的水。把意粉隔水下鍋同炒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9iXO10x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9iXO10x.jpg&h=702abdb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 把鰹魚粉和上一步留下煮意粉的水拌勻，倒入鍋中炒勻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bAPp96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bAPp96.jpg&h=110bbae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 下茄汁和糖炒勻，再加入巴馬臣芝士粉炒勻即可上碟。享用前可隨意灑上更多巴馬臣芝士粉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42h2niw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42h2niw.jpg&h=47c2548d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 吃辣的朋友可於加入茄汁時同時加入適量辣椒仔辣汁更惹味！"},{"pid":"69bde251acfe5e9caa07cd2b9261e21493d8e3cd","tid":36873,"uid":30698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368703e090a5ce9f80c5ec0ead692324f1b20096","tid":36873,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:09:51.000Z","msg":"點解係我煮完食完飯先有呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883f13933cec509998ef83ed6ff193229b2f694f","tid":36873,"uid":13614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"即刻好肚餓"},{"pid":"f73b6b7638806e69b9a32d40d5a716e4307f2b89","tid":36873,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"正評<br />\n唔洗講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4051542155b7d27432b08732234ca7ca5120365","tid":36873,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"正呀,一陣lunch就去食先"},{"pid":"c42bbd51f50a551bbc588bf65734dea27794dea8","tid":36873,"uid":59493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:44:48.000Z","msg":"路過揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe17c2dc709e365acf237d8fcfab8c89b470bc7","tid":36873,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正啊&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/asset