鮮味嘢，所以用咗鰹魚粉做鹹味代替鹽<br />\n如果無嘅同鹽都可以，不過當然要減量，但雞粉就唔好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6d0d77f944894645057e3f84faced8fac06874","tid":36873,"uid":4502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次呢個夠晒簡單易整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔用鰹魚粉得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今次個汁好少水份，唔使專登開盒雞湯，同埋因為材料比較簡單無咩鮮味嘢，所以用咗鰹魚粉做鹹味代替鹽<br />\n如果無嘅同鹽都可以，不過當然要減量，但雞粉就唔好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鰹魚粉邊度有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實呢個意粉可以加好多唔同餸落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e276947ba0b3c693e9386dd142e68d3bc3a4a47","tid":36873,"uid":65333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:35:07.000Z","msg":"好似好好食"},{"pid":"08b7ce64b1e80e7506fdb2e7a334c9dbf44d825e","tid":36873,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次呢個夠晒簡單易整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔用鰹魚粉得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今次個汁好少水份，唔使專登開盒雞湯，同埋因為材料比較簡單無咩鮮味嘢，所以用咗鰹魚粉做鹹味代替鹽<br />\n如果無嘅同鹽都可以，不過當然要減量，但雞粉就唔好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鰹魚粉邊度有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實呢個意粉可以加好多唔同餸落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好多地方都有㗎，大果啲超級市場例如sogo一田吉之島citysuper，某啲唔大間嘅百佳惠康都有，十二蚊店都見過<br />\n不過係啲牌仔有時未必寫同一個名 咩鰹魚粉/鰹魚素/柴魚粉/鰹魚風味調味料等等&hellip;&hellip;好多名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b77500694a870a5153785b331c21b4185b27b3","tid":36873,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:14:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似好好食</blockquote><br />\n我自己好鍾意<br />\n陣味好低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b194abd10425391bc46c6219f3b2be645bbe201","tid":36873,"uid":2794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9926d545688d9bac13c8d012090f294014223a","tid":36873,"uid":52585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:48:44.000Z","msg":"我要試食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15eb226ab5497c152e01d5960ff31ab22445b42","tid":36873,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=